The woman, 38 years old, 158 centimeters tall, thin, wears wedding dress, with a long white tail. She has a tattoo of the magnolia flower in the center of the neck and on her left side the tattoo of a dragonfly, on the right side she has a tattoo of a ladybug, she also has tattoos on his arms and the tattoo of a female elephant on her right thigh and under the tattoo he wears a white garter. He has reddish hair. The 44-year-old man, 165 centimeters tall, thin, wears a tight black suit, white shirt and thin black tie. He has tattooed under his right eye the word "wrong" and under his left eye the word "strong". He has tattooed on his neck an owl with outstretched wings, in neo-traditional style.
